Cell["\<\
In general, there are no nice formula known for the Kostka numbers.\
\>", "Notes",
 CellID->1995165925,ExpressionUUID->"9d275d52-173f-4e6e-83fe-5b26891fde5b"],

Cell["\<\
Since Q3 v4.2.4, the Kostka number is calculated by the Pieri rule.\
\>", "Notes",
